    "en": {
      "title": "Ranil Wickremesinghe sworn in as Sri Lanka Acting President",
      "author": "",
      "body_lines": [
        "ECONOMYNEXT \u2013 Sri Lanka Prime Minister Ranil Wickremesinghe was sworn in as Acting President following the resignation of President Gotabaya Rajapaksa, the prime minister\u2019s office said.",
        "Wickremesinghe was sworn in before Chief Justice Jayantha Jayasuirya Friday July 15, hours after Speaker Mahinda Yapa Abeywardena confirmed that he had accepted President Rajapaksa\u2019s letter of resignation on July 14.",
        "Abeywardena told reporters Friday morning that Wickremesinghe will serve as Acting President until parliament elects a new president from among its membership. (Colombo/July15/2022)"
      ],
